            <b> REENCUENTRO CON LAS NUEVAS GENERACIONES POST COVID-19</b>
        </h3>

        <div class="w3-col l4 m6 s12 w3-center">
            <div class="w3-display-container">
                <img src="assets/app/img/libros/libro_mini.jpeg" class="w3-image w3-round" width="335" height="471">

                <div class="w3-display-middle w3-hide w3-large" onclick="document.getElementById('preview_reencuentro').style.display='block'">
                    <button class="w3-button w3-white w3-text-green w3-hover-white w3-hover-text-blue">
                        Vista Previa del E-Book
